The paper proposes a novel approach for feature acquisition at test time using neural networks and autoencoders. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL) as these are the areas where such techniques are commonly used.
